Create procedure stg.DatesLoad 
AS
Insert into [ods].[dates] ( 
	[DateKey] 
	,[FullDate] 
	,[isWeekDay] 
	,[DayOfWeek] 
	,[DayOfMonth] 
	,[DayOfQuarter] 
	,[DayOfYear] 
	,[DayName] 
	,[WeekOfYear]
	,[WeekName] 
	,[MonthOfYear] 
	,[MonthName] 
	,[CalendarQuarter] 
	,[CalendarQuarterName] 
	,[CalendarYear] 
	,[FiscalMonth]
	,[FiscalMonthName] 
	,[FiscalQuarter] 
	,[FiscalQuarterName] 
	,[FiscalYear] 
)
Select 	[DateKey] 
	,[FullDate] 
	,[isWeekDay] 
	,[DayOfWeek] 
	,[DayOfMonth] 
	,[DayOfQuarter] 
	,[DayOfYear] 
	,REPLACE([DayName],'"','') AS [DayName] 
	,[WeekOfYear]
	,REPLACE([WeekName],'"','') AS [WeekName]
	,[MonthOfYear] 
	,REPLACE([MonthName] ,'"','') AS [MonthName]
	,[CalendarQuarter] 
	,REPLACE([CalendarQuarterName], '"', '') AS [CalendarQuarterName]
	,[CalendarYear] 
	,[FiscalMonth] 
	,REPLACE([FiscalMonthName] , '"','') AS [FiscalMonthName]
	,[FiscalQuarter] 
	,REPLACE([FiscalQuarterName] , '"', '') AS [FiscalQuarterName]
	,[FiscalYear] 
	from stg.azure_dates_stg
